{"tid":127183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又死一隻】滬男打街頭籃球重摔落地　一度傳斷頸命喪球場","createTime":"2017-02-20T02:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T03:00:36.000Z","uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"074aabae66889b42376e18eb1e70205646c49f27","tid":127183,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/photo/bkncn-20170219142555143-0219_05011_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170219%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170219142555143-0219_05011_001_01p.jpg&h=b59412ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上海市的籃球場發生了一宗恐怖意外！一名年輕男子在比賽期間摔倒，背部落地後一動不動，更一度傳出「斷頸」死亡，後經上海媒體證實，該名男子傷勢嚴重，未脫離性命危險。<br />\n<br />\n從網傳短片所見，該名男子衝向籃底騰空跳起，試圖阻止對手投籃，惟對方因急步停下，使該名男子凌空架在對方肩膊而失去平衡重摔在地。片中清楚看到該名男子背部重摔落地後，頸部及頭部先後撞在地面，一動不動，在場者隨即上前察看其情況。<br />\n<br />\n短片在網絡流傳後，一度傳出該名男子「斷頸」命喪籃球場，但經上海當地媒體證實，受傷男子現年25歲，目前正在上海市第六人民醫院接受治療。院方透露，傷者昨日下午4時左右送入神經外科急診，今日上午8時左右被收入病房，傷者顱內出血，目前生命體徵平穩，暫未脫離性命危險，需作進一步觀察。<br />\n<br />\n另外，廣西大學保衞處昨日發通報，指該校東校區一名男學生前日在打籃球時突然暈倒，被送院搶救後不治。據了解，死者為該校輕工與食品工程學院2015級碩士研究生。"},{"pid":"224d46bc70968118118f155f4a7540c3c2fa6700","tid":127183,"uid":79945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:10:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkncn-20170219142555143-0219_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170219%2Fbkncn-20170219142555143-0219_05011_001.html&d=IJ4Nzxd4hLWYFZk0XL5PgZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=dcf669c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170219/bkncn-20170219142555143-0219_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a8cc37bb4c2038742582f2d095334d69d94e5026","tid":127183,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:12:27.000Z","msg":"如果係香港街場 會唔會比人告誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66325b1e56ae1787642fc057f78856515ec4aa94","tid":127183,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"又死一隻係講緊中國人定藍波狗？"},{"pid":"671744d2a5e702b1e1166d015d5af887e6718919","tid":127183,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:14:20.000Z","msg":"監控到,連籃球場都有CCTV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9037df41342ffe51de4d88f5bb2ee028d73c053f","tid":127183,"uid":68141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"玩玩具死左可以揾邊個賠償?"},{"pid":"046cc718a66be7f78a06337116d06b4974af745b","tid":127183,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32067baacd31986fdc785bd91632bd3387e46d16","tid":127183,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>監控到,連籃球場都有CCTV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲球場係有人做自家管理，畀錢先可以入場打波，自然會有cctv監視場地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a6cabea1674e0355c24e825798e2af4a6a4a12","tid":127183,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:56:01.000Z","msg":"未死喎"},{"pid":"72ea29173e8788fbb8ddd361c17bd365f1314273","tid":127183,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"條友都算仆街ga la<br />\n晾鳩條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}